| ShortSummary        = Kirari Tsukishima saves a turtle stuck in a tree, and its owner, Seiji Hiwatari, gives her a ticket to a Ships concert. When she tries to attend the concert, Hiroto Kazama rips up her ticket and tells her that she and Seiji both live in different worlds. Determined, Kirari sneaks into the concert and discovers that Seiji and Hiroto are part of Ships. She declares on live television that she will become an idol.
| LineColor           =
